msgid "Image Editor"
msgstr "Eagarthóir Íomhá"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.showfoto.appdata.xml:9
msgid ""
"Showfoto is a fast Image Editor with powerful image editing tools. You can "
"use it to view your photographs and improve them. Showfoto is the standalone "
"image editor of the digiKam project."
msgstr ""
"Is Eagarthóir Íomhánna tapa é Showfoto le huirlisí eagarthóireachta íomhá "
"cumhachtacha. Is féidir leat é a úsáid chun do ghrianghraif a fheiceáil agus "
"iad a fheabhsú. Is é Showfoto an t-eagarthóir íomhá neamhspleách de chuid "
"thionscadal digiKam."

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
